(firstQuint)Comparing Use of the Glidescope Cobalt to Direct Laryngoscopy in Infants.

 We seek to study the intubation characteristics of a new video laryngoscope, the Glidescope Cobalt in children less than or equal to 1 yr of age.

 This evaluation would provide insight as to the efficacy of this device in facilitating intubation in infants.

